## Files Written / Verified

### 1. Flask Blueprint
**Path:** `/Users/michaelwegter/Desktop/Projects/mw-backend/edtech_blueprint.py`
**Status:** Verified complete (497 lines, syntax OK, no em/en dashes)
**Blueprint variable:** `edtech_bp`
**URL prefix:** `/api/edtech`

**Endpoints implemented:**
- `POST  /api/edtech/login`                  -- credential check, returns JWT with role
- `GET   /api/edtech/student`                -- student info (both roles)
- `GET   /api/edtech/grades`                 -- student grades (both roles)
- `PATCH /api/edtech/grades/<id>`            -- update a grade (teacher only)
- `GET   /api/edtech/activities`             -- activity feed (both roles)
- `POST  /api/edtech/activities`             -- create activity (teacher only)
- `GET   /api/edtech/messages`               -- full message thread (both roles)
- `POST  /api/edtech/messages`               -- send a message (both roles)
- `GET   /api/edtech/messages/unread-count`  -- unread count for polling (both roles)
- `PATCH /api/edtech/messages/read-all`      -- mark all from other role as read
- `PATCH /api/edtech/messages/<id>/read`     -- mark one message as read

**Storage:** SQLite at `data/mw.db`, tables created lazily, seed idempotent (checks COUNT=0)
**Auth:** bcrypt password hash/verify, PyJWT HS256 tokens, 24-hour TTL
**Demo accounts seeded:**
  - parent@demo.edu / ParentDemo1 (parent role, name: Robert Johnson)
  - teacher@demo.edu / TeachDemo1 (teacher role, name: Mrs. Rivera)
  - Student: Alex Johnson, Grade 7
  - Grades: Math A(95), English B+(88), Science A-(91), History B(84), Art A(97), PE A+(100)
  - 4 seed activities, 2 seed messages

