### 3. Demo Frontend
**Path:** `/Users/michaelwegter/Desktop/Projects/michaelwegter.com/public/demos/edtech-school-connect-web-portal/index.html`
**Status:** Verified complete (1548 lines, no em/en dashes)
**Live URL (after deploy):** `https://michaelwegter.com/demos/edtech-school-connect-web-portal/`

**Features implemented (feature richness 10/10):**
- Role-based login (parent vs teacher) with demo hint cards (click to fill)
- Parent dashboard: student banner with GPA, top-3 grade stats, recent activity feed, messages shortcut
- Teacher dashboard: class average, updates count, unread message count
- Grades view (parent): card grid with letter/score/progress bars + Chart.js radar chart (6 axes)
- Grade management (teacher): editable table with inline save + radar chart (live-updates on save)
- Activity feed (parent): full chronological feed with color-coded category badges
- Post Update (teacher): category selector (Academic/Event/Attendance/Announcement/Behavior) + text area, posts to API and refreshes feed
- Messages: iMessage-style bubble thread, compose with Enter-to-send, auto-scroll on new message
- Unread badge: 4-second polling of `/api/edtech/messages/unread-count`, badge on nav and mobile tabs
- PHP info bar: dark banner explaining Flask-to-PHP/Laravel mapping
- Mobile responsive: sidebar collapses to fixed bottom tab bar at 768px
- Toast notifications for save/post/error feedback
- XSS-safe `esc()` on all user-supplied content

**Design system (bespoke, not michaelwegter.com):**
- Primary: #1A56DB | Accent: #0E9F6E | Warning: #E3A008 | Danger: #E02424
- Bg: #F9FAFB | Card: #FFFFFF | Border: #E5E7EB
- Fonts: Nunito (headings) + Inter (body) via Google Fonts CDN
- Chart.js 4.4.0 via jsDelivr CDN

