## PHP Mapping (for proposal)

| Demo layer          | PHP/Laravel production equivalent     |
|---------------------|---------------------------------------|
| Flask blueprint     | Laravel Controller + Routes (web.php) |
| SQLite tables       | MySQL/PostgreSQL with Eloquent ORM    |
| PyJWT tokens        | Laravel Sanctum or Passport           |
| Vanilla JS frontend | Vue.js, Livewire, or keep vanilla JS  |
| 4s client polling   | Laravel Echo + Pusher WebSockets      |
| Static file serving | Laravel on shared hosting or a VPS    |

